"{\"uid\": \"africa.espn.com-olympics-story-_-id-40625418-2024-olympic-opening-ceremony-outfits-usa-haiti-mongolia-chinese-taipei\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"You have come to the ESPN Africa edition, for other ESPN editions, click above.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 79, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 52, \"end\": 56, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0205178344219833e-14, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Theopening ceremonyfor the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris offers the world's top athletes a moment to shine well before any podium appearances.\", \"from\": 81, \"to\": 223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 132, \"end\": 137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.929206957579581e-34, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike most of the upcoming Olympic events, gold, silver, and bronze will not be the highlights on Friday.\", \"from\": 225, \"to\": 331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, Olympians will proudly wear denim, cashmere, cotton, and other fabrics in their opening ceremony uniforms.\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 447, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Together, these ensembles highlight the intersection of fashion and sports, offering a global stage for cultural expression and unity.\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are some must-see opening ceremony uniforms from around the world:  Designer: Ralph Lauren  America is renowned for its red, white, and blue, but this time the spotlight is on the blue.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 668, \"end\": 680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.9999999822966857, \"rank\": 1.7703269257048827e-08, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The nation's athletes will don navy blazers, striped button-up shirts, and denim jeans.\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 851, \"end\": 856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denim\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"denim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denim\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denim\"}, {\"begin\": 857, \"end\": 862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"jeans\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jeans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These blazers are adorned with patriotic trim and display the Olympic logo.\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 939, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Ralph Lauren (@ralphlauren)  Designer: Sportscraft  The country's national colors of green and gold provide the base shades for the ensemble.\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 1099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 958, \"end\": 970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"score\": 0.9999999822966857, \"rank\": 1.7703269257048827e-08, \"text\": \"Ralph Lauren\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Lauren\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both men and women will wear a green linen blazer paired with stone-colored shorts or a green and gold ombre pleated skirt.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The blazer features the Australian Olympians' Oath, on the inside jacket pocket and the names of all 301 Australian Summer Olympic champions are inscribed on the jacket lining.\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1250, \"end\": 1260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9996923499495707, \"rank\": 0.0003077443079625539, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1331, \"end\": 1341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9996923499495707, \"rank\": 0.0003077443079625539, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The story behind our tenth@SportscraftAustralian Olympic Team Opening Ceremony uniform accompanied by@VolleyAustraliafootwear \\ud83d\\udc9a\\ud83d\\udc9b\\ud83c\\udde6\\ud83c\\uddfa \\ud83c\\uddeb\\ud83c\\uddf7Bring on 26 July, 2024.\\ud83d\\udc49https://t.co/M9JrnxCMuZ#AllezAUSpic.twitter.com/Yojqh17Zw4  \\ud83d\\udc9a Goosebumps \\ud83d\\udc9b For an athlete there is nothing like putting on the Australian Olympic Team jacket.#AllezAUS|@Sportscraft|@VolleyAustralia|@WaterPoloAus|@AusVolley|@Paddle_Auspic.twitter.com/B6sH9eGm2p  This morning we launched into 1\\ufe0f\\u20e30\\ufe0f\\u20e30\\ufe0f\\u20e3 days to#Paris2024by revealing the Australian Olympic Team Opening Ceremony uniform at the stunning Clovelly Beach in Sydney \\ud83c\\udde6\\ud83c\\uddfa\\ud83d\\udc9a\\ud83d\\udc9b#AllezAUS|@Sportscraft|@VolleyAustraliapic.twitter.com/241iuj2OzW  Designer: Lululemon  Thanks to Lululemon, Canadian athletes will not have to choose between style and comfort.\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 2168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.03239350089127e-20, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1906, \"end\": 1929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.03239350089127e-20, \"text\": \"Australian Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1930, \"end\": 1946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.2145710078684933e-12, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}, {\"begin\": 1971, \"end\": 1979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clovelly\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.417835022713685e-19, \"text\": \"Clovelly\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clovelly\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clovelly\"}, {\"begin\": 2081, \"end\": 2090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lululemon\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\"}, {\"begin\": 2102, \"end\": 2111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lululemon\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lululemon_Athletica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athleisure brand prioritized inclusivity and adaptability while celebrating the country's history.\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The red outfit features a hand-drawn \\\"tapestry of pride\\\" in the fabric, incorporating 10 animals -- nine representing Canada's provinces and one symbolizing France.\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team Canada's LOOKS for#Paris2024, a thread \\ud83e\\uddf5Opening ceremony \\ud83c\\udde8\\ud83c\\udde6 \\ud83c\\udf86@TeamCanada@CDNParalympics@lululemonpic.twitter.com/ApjVRofcyz  Designer: Justin Chou  Chinese Taipei's Olympic opening ceremony is inspired by artist Paul Chaing's \\\"Mountain Range of Taiwan\\\" painting.\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2442, \"end\": 2448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0445776223845596e-15, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2595, \"end\": 2606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Chou\", \"score\": 0.9999911657204444, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Justin Chou\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Chou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Chou\"}, {\"begin\": 2595, \"end\": 2606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Chou\", \"score\": 0.9999911657204444, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Justin Chou\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Chou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Chou\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It further pays homage to the country by highlighting its national flowers and traditional good luck tokens.\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2814, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by JUST IN XX (@justinxx_official)  Designer: Alpine Pro  The Czech Republic's Olympic opening ceremony attire draws inspiration from its national flag, which consists of two horizontal stripes of white over red with a blue triangle at the hoist.\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 3076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Underneath the white and blue outer layer is a polo shirt featuring a gradient design of all three national shades, complemented by blue slacks.\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3221, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by C\\u030cesky\\u0301 olympijsky\\u0301 ty\\u0301m \\ud83c\\udde8\\ud83c\\uddff (@olympijskytym)  Designer: Berluti  Men and women of the host country will wear tailored midnight-blue tuxedo jackets and matching pants (or option of a wrap skirt for women)  paired with white button-up shirts.\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Inside each item, the phrase \\\"Artisan of all victories\\\" is embroidered on a label with gold thread.\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The ensemble will be accessorized with patterned pocket handkerchiefs, scarves, and hand-varnished belts, along with lapel pins in blue and red, reflecting the key colors of the French flag.\", \"from\": 3582, \"to\": 3772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"[#Paris2024]M\\u00e9lina Robert-Michon, Florent Manaudou, Nantenin Keita et Alexis Hanquinquant ont \\u00e9t\\u00e9 choisis par leurs pairs pour repr\\u00e9senter la France lors des Jeux Olympiques et Paralympiques de Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 3774, \"to\": 3979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3793, \"end\": 3795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hash_(EP)\", \"score\": 0.9999999947203833, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"[#\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hash_(EP)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hash_(EP)\"}, {\"begin\": 3805, \"end\": 3825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9lina_Robert-Michon\", \"score\": 0.9999999999454303, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"M\\u00e9lina Robert-Michon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9lina_Robert-Michon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9lina_Robert-Michon\"}, {\"begin\": 3805, \"end\": 3825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9lina_Robert-Michon\", \"score\": 0.9999999999454303, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"M\\u00e9lina Robert-Michon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9lina_Robert-Michon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e9lina_Robert-Michon\"}, {\"begin\": 3827, \"end\": 3834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florent_Manaudou\", \"score\": 0.999992521573173, \"rank\": 7.4784825904348915e-06, \"text\": \"Florent\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florent_Manaudou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florent_Manaudou\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Les athl\\u00e8tes ont exprim\\u00e9 leur joie et l'honneur que cela repr\\u00e9sente...pic.twitter.com/29UI2kyYLZ  Designer: Ben Sherman  For the opening ceremony, Team Great Britain will don a white bomber jacket with navy sleeves, adorned with a floral embroidery on the back.\", \"from\": 3980, \"to\": 4241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4012, \"end\": 4015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario\", \"score\": 0.9999999999618012, \"rank\": 3.7772721751110656e-11, \"text\": \"ont\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario\"}, {\"begin\": 4182, \"end\": 4195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flight_jacket\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"bomber jacket\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flight_jacket\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flight_jacket\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This design, incorporating the rose, thistle, daffodil, and shamrock, symbolizes the unity of the United Kingdom's four nations of \\u200b\\u200bEngland, Scotland, Wales, and Northern Ireland.\", \"from\": 4242, \"to\": 4422, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4394, \"end\": 4401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England\", \"score\": 0.9999980492376308, \"rank\": 1.610814568550218e-06, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England\"}, {\"begin\": 4403, \"end\": 4411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\", \"score\": 0.9999999999026841, \"rank\": 9.448651731645489e-11, \"text\": \"Scotland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scotland\"}, {\"begin\": 4413, \"end\": 4418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"score\": 0.9999998158100595, \"rank\": 1.8077847728082736e-07, \"text\": \"Wales\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wales\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ensemble will be completed with a knitted polo that bears a geometric red-and-blue pattern and light blue trousers.\", \"from\": 4423, \"to\": 4542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Opening Ceremony wear features tailored pieces for all athletes representing Team GB, including a bomber style jacket.On the back of the jacket is a specially designed and embroidered four-nation floral design.pic.twitter.com/r4vkF4N5Om  Designer: Jaspe  Guatemala's design features a vibrant palette of green and blue.\", \"from\": 4544, \"to\": 4867, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Women will wear green dresses paired with blue vests, while men will sport blue button-up shirts and green slacks.\", \"from\": 4868, \"to\": 4982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To complete the look, both ensembles are accessorized with blue hats and black shoulder pads adorned with colorful traditional prints.\", \"from\": 4983, \"to\": 5117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83e\\udd29 Presentamos la indumentaria que portar\\u00e1n nuestros atletas en la ceremonia de inauguraci\\u00f3n de los Juegos Ol\\u00edmpicos de#Par\\u00eds2024\\ud83c\\uddeb\\ud83c\\uddf7, dise\\u00f1ada para representar la fuerza, la resiliencia y la belleza de nuestro pa\\u00eds.\\u00a1Con orgullo, con valent\\u00eda, con Guatemala en el alma!\", \"from\": 5119, \"to\": 5385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5299, \"end\": 5308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Fuerza\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"la fuerza\", \"types\": [\"Q482994\", \"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Fuerza\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Fuerza\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83d\\udc99\\ud83e\\udd0dpic.twitter.com/N86pwMCAZL  Designer: Stella Jean  Local artist Philippe Dodard's \\\"Passage\\\" painting takes center stage in the uniform's skirt and trousers with a dynamic print.\", \"from\": 5386, \"to\": 5565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5386, \"end\": 5395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala\", \"score\": 0.9999999996571205, \"rank\": 3.42362162032295e-10, \"text\": \"Guatemala\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guatemala\"}, {\"begin\": 5402, \"end\": 5406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alma_Mahler\", \"score\": 0.9999978246447441, \"rank\": 2.1727203886865797e-06, \"text\": \"alma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alma_Mahler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alma_Mahler\"}, {\"begin\": 5450, \"end\": 5461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stella Jean\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The women will complement the vibrant pattern with a woven shirt and belted blazer.\", \"from\": 5566, \"to\": 5649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Men, on the other hand, will wear light bluefield jackets inspired by the classic Haitian Guayabera shirt.\", \"from\": 5650, \"to\": 5756, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Stella Jean (@stellajean_sj_)  Designer: Laura Weber  Ireland's all-white outfits celebrate the country's century-long participation in the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 5758, \"to\": 5929, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5799, \"end\": 5810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stella Jean\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stella_Jean\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each athlete's jacket includes a distinctive embroidered patch on the sleeve, showcasing a beaded, sequined, and stone-studded design of the athlete.\", \"from\": 5931, \"to\": 6080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As a symbol of good luck, the jackets also feature a shamrock brooch crafted from four embroidered four-leaf clovers.\", \"from\": 6081, \"to\": 6198, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TEAM IRELAND OPENING CEREMONY WEARIrish designed, made, and worn for the@paris2024Olympic Opening Ceremony in one week \\ud83e\\udd47Team Ireland x Laura Weber#TeamIreland|#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/J9rldrojx8  Designer: Unknown  Kazakhstani athletes will sport white shirts with ties beneath striking blue blazers, complemented by white skirts or trousers.\", \"from\": 6200, \"to\": 6543, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Adorning the bottom of the blazers and the sides of the pants are a series of symbols, each rich with historical significance.\", \"from\": 6544, \"to\": 6670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the illustrative elements are \\\"m\\u00fcyiz\\\" (horns), embodying strength, courage, and protection, while \\\"kaz moiyn\\\" (gooseneck) captures the essence of flexibility, agility, and grace.\", \"from\": 6671, \"to\": 6855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Traditional ceremony of presenting the State Flag of the Republic of Kazakhstan to the Olympic team \\ud83c\\uddf0\\ud83c\\uddffSee you soon, Paris!\", \"from\": 6857, \"to\": 6979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6939, \"end\": 6947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9983691030411155, \"rank\": 0.0012997970640425214, \"text\": \"Republic\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"@olympic_kzpic.twitter.com/wPaNSUHaAl  Designer: Unknown  Malaysia's opening ceremony uniforms honor the Malayan tiger, the country's national animal.\", \"from\": 6979, \"to\": 7129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7075, \"end\": 7091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 3.090660692921132e-13, \"text\": \"opening ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The jacket proudly displays an eye-catching print of orange and black stripes, echoing the tiger's majestic appearance.\", \"from\": 7130, \"to\": 7249, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The ensemble is finished off with sleek black pants.\", \"from\": 7250, \"to\": 7302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"https://t.co/LeJ62UedVWpic.twitter.com/Pypuj6laVI  Designer: Men's Fashion  The Mexican Olympic team will don a striking pink and white outfit featuring sleeve prints inspired by the cities of Oaxaca, San Miguel de Allende, and Michoac\\u00e1n.\", \"from\": 7304, \"to\": 7542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7524, \"end\": 7530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oaxaca\", \"score\": 0.9984410636971545, \"rank\": 0.001561370379588195, \"text\": \"Oaxaca\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oaxaca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oaxaca\"}, {\"begin\": 7